  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🔥 <strong>Relive the golden age of co-op Arcade games with Kemono Heroes!</strong> 🔥</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Imagine the thrill of classic arcade nights—blazing through levels, side by side with your friends, dodging, slashing, and unleashing chaos on screen. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2787700/extras/1785a516026540c4b9b175d775f8621e.avif?t=1764581116\" width=700 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Kemono Heroes</i> brings back that magic, blending <strong>run ‘n gun mayhem</strong> with <strong>fast-paced ninja action</strong> and <strong>fluffy, badass warriors</strong> straight out of a 16-bit dream!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2787700/extras/46b944beb90ea6019f4cfa9ffa5509c2.avif?t=1764581116\" width=700 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⚔️ Go solo and test your skills with three difficulty levels, or grab up to <strong>three friends</strong> and take on the adventure <strong>together</strong>, just like the old days, same screen, same energy, same unforgettable moments.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2787700/extras/87541e792b1497318f044d364ce1fe19.avif?t=1764581116\" width=700 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From the creators of <strong><i>A Hole New World</i></strong>, this is our <strong>love letter to classic co-op gaming.</strong> We went from 8-bit to <strong>a full-on 16-bit arcade experience</strong>, packed with <strong>4 unique heroes</strong>, <strong>unlockable weapons</strong>, and <strong>non-stop action</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2787700/extras/7d990f0390f3b707fb10b0f26378c2e4.avif?t=1764581116\" width=700 height=250 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Run 'n Slash 'n Gun!</strong> Lightning-fast action that keeps you on your toes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>1-4 player local co-op!</strong> Play alone or with friends—teamwork is key!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gorgeous 16-bit pixel art!</strong> A visual feast straight from the golden era.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>4 distinct heroes!</strong> Each with their own special skills and style.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>4 worlds, 3 stages each!</strong> Different biomes, new enemies, fresh challenges.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unlockable weapons and powers!</strong> Upgrade your arsenal as you fight.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Tons of action and pure, unfiltered fun!</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get ready to <strong>dash, slash, and relive the golden age of arcade co-op</strong> with <i>Kemono Heroes</i>! 🕹️🐾 Are you in?</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🔥 <strong>Relive the golden age of co-op Arcade games with Kemono Heroes!</strong> 🔥</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Imagine the thrill of classic arcade nights—blazing through levels, side by side with your friends, dodging, slashing, and unleashing chaos on screen. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2787700/extras/1785a516026540c4b9b175d775f8621e.avif?t=1764581116\" width=700 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Kemono Heroes</i> brings back that magic, blending <strong>run ‘n gun mayhem</strong> with <strong>fast-paced ninja action</strong> and <strong>fluffy, badass warriors</strong> straight out of a 16-bit dream!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2787700/extras/46b944beb90ea6019f4cfa9ffa5509c2.avif?t=1764581116\" width=700 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⚔️ Go solo and test your skills with three difficulty levels, or grab up to <strong>three friends</strong> and take on the adventure <strong>together</strong>, just like the old days, same screen, same energy, same unforgettable moments.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2787700/extras/87541e792b1497318f044d364ce1fe19.avif?t=1764581116\" width=700 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From the creators of <strong><i>A Hole New World</i></strong>, this is our <strong>love letter to classic co-op gaming.</strong> We went from 8-bit to <strong>a full-on 16-bit arcade experience</strong>, packed with <strong>4 unique heroes</strong>, <strong>unlockable weapons</strong>, and <strong>non-stop action</strong>.</p><p cla